Project Name
============



Requirements
------------
- PHP 7+
- composer
- MySQL / MariaDB / PostgreSQL
- Node.js (dev)
- Gulp (dev)



Install
-------

1.  Create a .env file by duplicating `.env.example` and
    filling in the appropriate environment specific values

2.  Run `composer install`

3.  Use appropriate config file based on the server software.
    Eg. if using Apache, duplicate `serverconfigs/apache-dev/sample.htacces`
    into `web/.htacces`.



Development
-----------

1.  Run `cd assets`

2.  Run `npm install`

3.  Run `gulp`

